      <scopecontent id="aspace_scope">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Jean Harris Papers consist of correspondence; clippings; printed material; research material on correctional systems; writings; legal documents; memorabilia; audiotapes; video tapes (of television interviews); and her trial record. The vast majority of the materials date from 1980.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
